</List><Paragraph>语法：<TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">/swing &lt;entity selector&gt; &lt;mainhand|offhand&gt;</TextBox></Paragraph><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">对 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">swing</TextBox> 的更改</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">现在两个参数都可缺省，并回调到如下默认值：</Paragraph></ListItem>
