<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">若为 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">true</TextBox>，则包含 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">material</TextBox> 原料匹配物品的格子数量会被加入到结果堆叠的最终数量中</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">minecraft:crafting_dye</TextBox></Paragraph><List>
