</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H3}">着色器与后处理效果</Paragraph><Section Style="{StaticResource devnoteQuote}">
  <Paragraph FontWeight="Bold">
    开发者注释
    <Paragraph.Foreground>
      <Binding Path="BorderBrush" RelativeSource="{RelativeSource Mode=FindAncestor, AncestorType=Section}" />
    </Paragraph.Foreground>
  </Paragraph>
  
<Paragraph> 虽然在资源包中可以做到，覆盖核心着色器被视为不受支持并非预期的资源包特性。这些着色器是游戏内部实现的一部分，因此可能会随着内部演进随时改变。我们理解覆盖核心着色器被用于很多很酷的资源包特性，其中很多缺乏受支持的替代方案。我们希望未来提供更好且受支持的替代方案。</Paragraph>

</Section><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">着色器</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/rendertype_item_entity_translucent_cull</TextBox> 着色器已被移除，改用 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/entity</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/rendertype_entity_alpha</TextBox> 与 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/rendertype_entity_decal</TextBox> 着色器已被 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/entity</TextBox> 中实现的 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">DISSOLVE</TextBox> 标志取代</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">物品渲染（UI 与世界中）已从 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/entity</TextBox> 分离到新的 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">core/item</TextBox> 着色器</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">block.vsh</TextBox> 与 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">terrain.vsh</TextBox> 着色器不再接收 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">Normal</TextBox> 顶点属性</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource H4}">光照贴图着色器</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">lightmap.fsh</TextBox> 着色器进行了大量修改：</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">LightmapInfo</TextBox> uniform 新增两个字段：</Paragraph><List>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">BlockLightTint</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}"><TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">NightVisionColor</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
</List></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph Style="{StaticResource Lp}">移除了 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">AmbientLightFactor</TextBox> 字段，其值现已预乘进 <TextBox Style="{StaticResource InlineCode}">AmbientColor</TextBox></Paragraph></ListItem>
